{"type":"message","id":"c54404db","parentId":"6f8afcb4","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:04:51.218Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 00:04 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下4个道简网络相关行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n- 搜索最新资讯，优先2026年3月的新闻\n- 每个领域找2-3条关键动态\n- 整理成结构化信息，包含：标题、来源、摘要要点\n- 输出语言为中文\n\n请直接返回搜索结果，不要使用浏览器工具"}],"timestamp":1774713891215}}
{"type":"message","id":"91dc51fe","parentId":"c54404db","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:04:57.709Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to search for the latest industry news (March 2026) for 4 areas related to 道简网络's business:\n1. Enterprise Digital Transformation\n2. Smart Security\n3. Network System Integration\n4. IT Operations Services\n\nI need to use web search to find these. Let me use the miaoda-web-search skill or web-search skill to find this information.\n\nLet me first read the web-search skill to understand how to use it properly.","thinkingSignature":"9955e526a355c1c8e05029b7bf2a85b627da528b0c56012179ff056b226eece0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v62keh7wqaze_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":136,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42112,"totalTokens":42365,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.00016319999999999998,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.005053439999999999,"total":0.0052517399999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774713891217}}
{"type":"message","id":"f88e2aa1","parentId":"91dc51fe","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:04:57.715Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_v62keh7wqaze_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774713897712}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5c75d19","parentId":"f88e2aa1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:05:03.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the tool. I need to use `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` to search for news in each of the 4 areas. Let me search for all 4 topics in parallel.","thinkingSignature":"75b88f4e0ddfeaedf45debd3f98c35e339a8abe665c5abfdbc22f8bc7e9f3088"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hh7krkulxo64_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 最新动态 2026年3月\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hh7krkulxo64_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业动态 2026年3月\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hh7krkulxo64_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 行业新闻 2026年3月\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hh7krkulxo64_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务 行业动态 2026年3月\" --output json 2>/dev/null | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":931,"output":259,"cacheRead":41949,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43139,"cost":{"input":0.0002793,"output":0.00031079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0012584699999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00184857}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774713897715}}
